latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#styledbyrishi

Abhishek Gupta Benares
@abhishekguptabenares 

Homecoming AW 21

Growing up in Benares had a profound cultural and artistic impact on Abhishek Gupta and this collection embodies those aesthetic qualities. Using traditional handloom fabrics juxtaposed with fine appliqué, pleating, intricate thread  embroidery & fine quilting, each garment is a masterpiece with assiduous craftsmanship, impeccable cut and fine tailoring, finished to invisible detail.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Late Night Musings
latestIgtvVideos.caption: It's 3:30 in the morning, a month into the the lockdown and I'm thinking of @radhikashankar and the many nights of karaoke-ing with her. My karaoke nights were that one moment when I'd let go of my social anxiety and belt out my favorites at the top of my lungs, those vocal cords lubricated by multiple LIITs, and the confidence bolstered by the minimal lighting of the pub/club/cafe. In this period of uncertainty, and isolation, I deeply miss my happy times of love and laughter shared with friends, and maybe that's what gave me the strength to put this one out here, minus the alcohol and the shadows. Radhika and I would sing this number together. It was OUR song. I miss you girl, and I can't wait for you and me and the rest of the world to get back on our feet and sing our hearts out once again. ❤️ @madonna #madonna #borderline #acoustic
